description: Moneta Gold Inc. operates as a resource exploration company in Canada. The company explores for gold deposits. Its flagship project is the Tower gold project located to the east of Timmins. The company was formerly known as Moneta Porcupine Mines Inc. and changed its name to Moneta Gold Inc. in August 2021. Moneta Gold Inc. was incorporated in 1910 and is headquartered in Timmins, Canada.
